doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, minimum-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=0")
    title Shaun Byrne: Full Stack Product Designer
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='src/css/style.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet prefetch', href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Swiper/4.2.2/css/swiper.min.css')
      
  body
    section.intro
      .container
        h1.intro Shaun Byrne 
        p.sub-heading Product Design Professional in Melbourne, 🇦🇺.
        p.about I thrive on bringing multidisciplinary teams together to deliver products through design thinking and lean UX principles. 

        a.scroll(href="#section-two") 👇

    section.my-expereince#section-two
      .swiper-container
        .swiper-wrapper
          .swiper-slide
            .container
              h1 My Strengths
              p Throughout my career, I have been fortunate to experience, learn about and use some of the most useful tools, methods and approaches that have helped me become the designer I am today.
              p 👉
          .swiper-slide 
            .container
              h1 First and foremost, I'm a designer. 
              p I have an inherit need to understand what the user wants and fullfill that need with valuable flows and journeys. I really enjoy doing it collaborativly with other designers and product teams. 
          .swiper-slide 
            .container
              h1 Data Informed Decison Maker
              p I value and use qualitative and quantitiative information gathering techniques to help inform better decisions. From longitudinal studies, to fine tuned A/B and multi variant experimentation, I've used it. 
          .swiper-slide 
            .container
              h1 Collaborative Contributor
              p We're all unique. Our collecitve knowledge is what harnesses the power for truely amazing experiences for users. I thrive on an inclusive journey to deliver for our users. 
          .swiper-slide 
            .container
              h1 Bridger of Gaps
              p I've worked extensively with technical teams. From engineers, Data scientists to other desingers, I have come to understand the methods and language that equips me with the ability to bridge gaps other designers cannot.  
              
        .swiper-pagination
        
        .swiper-button-next
        .swiper-button-prev

    section.contact
      .container
        h1 Interested in a chat?
        p Currently I am focused on my role at #[a.redbubble(href="http://www.redbubble.com") Redbubble], but I always have time for a ☕️ or 💬. Get in contact if you want to learn more about me, my work, or you want really good Melbourne café suggestions. 
        a.button(href="mailto:byrnecore+portfolio@gmail.com") 👍🏻 Yep, let's chat

    section.social
      .container
        .social-profiles
          h1 Learn more about me
          p To see what my life is about, here are all my social profiles 😱. You might even find some of my professional work too. 
          .links
            a.profile.behance
            a.profile.dribbble  
            a.profile.linkedin  
            a.profile.github  
            a.profile.medium  
            a.profile.instagram  
            a.profile.spotify  
            a.profile.twitter  
            a.profile.pinterest 
            
    section.footer
      .container
        p Designed and built by #[a(href="#") Shaun Byrne] © 2017 | Melbourne, 🇦🇺, 🌏.

